; One week ago, the Serious Fraud Office, a government prosecution agency, began investigating Mirror Group Newspapers PLC's pension fund assets and related matters.
The company says about $630 million was taken from its pension fund without authority.; Kevin Maxwell spoke with the Daily Mirror as he flew to New York on Tuesday for talks on the future of the Daily News, which his father bought in March.
